Added projectile class, Progress on towers shooting projectiles
Towers target enemies and shoot projectiles at them, enemies take damage, and die, added ProjectileEntity interface
Spawns next wave after you defeat all enemies from the current one, when you defeat all waves it draws "You win" on the screen.
